---
description: PHP and Symfony bundle rules
globs:
  - "src/**/*.php"
  - "src/**/*.yaml"
  - "src/**/*.yml"
alwaysApply: false
---

Target compatibility: PHP >=8.2 and Symfony 6.4 / 7 / 8.

Prefer:
- strict typing and explicit return types
- PSR-12 coding style
- constructor injection for services
- PHPDoc in English for public APIs

Do not introduce BC breaks unless explicitly requested.
